name: Ampel Hill Homestay
address: Ped, Nusa Penida, Klungkung Regency, Bali 80771, Indonesia
review 1: Beautiful homestay on a farm. Secluded but manages to have strong enough internet for me to take 3 hours of video calls. Very kind owner who tends to the gardens and farm. Would highly recommend this place!
review 2: Beautiful and peacefull place with a direct view on Agung Mount. Very friendly and helpfull host. The room was very clean and the bed confortable. You can eat your breakfast in the restaurant in front of the homestay. The small road next by can be noisy at 6.30 am (scooters), so the use of earplugs can be a good idea for light sleepers. 10 minutes from Tokyapeh airbour by scooter. Top! Thanks!
review 3: We loved staying here! Arie was so kind and helpful. He helped us rent scooters for the weekend and made us breakfast everyday. The place is beautiful with a great view for sunset. Highly recommend!
review 4: Best view of bali and only place to enjoy sunset from penida.
